1. save your code
2. plug your adafruit
3. reset by press "reset" button twice (should light up all red and green)
4. When reset, you should be able to see it in your Finder/My Computer
5. Drag and drop
6. it automatically starts the program 


Warnings:
- if you reset your device and put a new code in it, it deletes your previous program
- if your program will start on switch moved, the switch has to be in inactive position before starting the program,
  otherwise it won't work and you have to reset
